{"id":152134,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/用量子纠缠主持婚礼/","date":"2011-05-13T21:00:32Z","modified":"2011-05-13T21:00:32Z","title":"用量子纠缠主持婚礼","content":"<p>概念艺术家Jonathon Keats借鉴物理学，设想出一种超教派的婚礼形式：量子纠缠。 Keats设计出一种量子纠缠仪器，安装在太阳窗上，使用可调棱镜，让阳光穿透用β-barium borate制成的非线性光学晶体，将太阳光分成成对的纠缠光子，分别落在太阳窗下仰视的一对新人身上，他们的脸将被纠缠光子轰击一分钟，在光电效应下他们的皮肤深深刻上了量子纠缠的神秘烙印。如此，神圣的婚礼典礼完成，新人们在量子纠缠的誓言下结成永恒的一对。请保持虔诚，不要持有怀疑心态，怀疑将会干扰和破坏量子婚姻。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/14ca2646/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E7%94%A8%E9%87%8F%E5%AD%90%E7%BA%A0%E7%BC%A0%E4%B8%BB%E6%8C%81%E5%A9%9A%E7%A4%BC&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fscience.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F12%2F1438205%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E7%94%A8%E9%87%8F%E5%AD%90%E7%BA%A0%E7%BC%A0%E4%B8%BB%E6%8C%81%E5%A9%9A%E7%A4%BC&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fscience.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F12%2F1438205%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101090844270/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/14ca2646/a2.htm\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101090844270/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/14ca2646/a2.img\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=B9Dc0EEzrk0:knRc2OMAXgA:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=B9Dc0EEzrk0:knRc2OMAXgA:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n</p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewU